        "description": "XR-specific UX \nWe developed and tested the UX to ensure the user benefits from the new environment. A user can adjust their assistant and dashboard to where it’s convenient. \n\nTutorial \nThe tutorial shouldn’t be too long or too short: we need to explain all the peculiarities of the app and not get our audience bored. We tested the tutorial on people with little experience in VR/XR, and did our best to find that balance between the timing and detail. \n\nSalsa coach \nThe coach has human-like features: lip sync, body language, and natural leg movement. During the tutorial the coach provides a detailed explanation of how to use the app, making it feel like you're getting personalized coaching from a real person.\n\nLanguage\nNow the app is in English, other languages are coming soon. ",
